<bibRefCitation id="EFB0D4FFFF88D933BAEE2DF1FA178797" author="Naudin, C. V." box="[1221,1445,1922,1949]" pageId="8" pageNumber="129" pagination="83 - 246" refId="ref9577" refString="Naudin, C. V. (1850) Melastomacearum monographicae descriptiones. [series 3] Annales des Sciences Naturelles; Botanique 16: 83 - 246." type="journal article" year="1850">Naudin (1850: 171)</bibRefCitation>
